meta.name: Nikola Jokić
meta.description: Nikola Jokic sees angles that the rest of us could only dream of. The Denver Nuggets center takes an entry pass against the Cleveland Cavaliers, dribbles to the baseline then wraps a pass around the defense to a wide open JaMychal Green while falling out of bounds. Jokic finished the game with a 16-point, 12-rebound, 10-assist triple-double on February 19, 2021.

meta.name: Kendrick Nunn
meta.description: If the defense doesn’t give up a lane, make your own. Miami Heat guard Kendrick Nunn works against Denver Nuggets defender Jamal Murray in the corner, hits him with an explosive first step, then rounds the corner on him and takes it to the rack. Nunn put up 17 points in the January 27, 2021 contest.
